.TH SPACEGL_SERVER 1 "2026-04-19" "SpaceGL @VERSION@" "SpaceGL Manual"
.SH NAME
spacegl_server \- SpaceGL galaxy server daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B spacegl_server
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B spacegl_server
is the central game server for the SpaceGL multi-user 3D space engine.
It manages galaxy state, player sessions, NPC entities, and secure
communication channels via shared memory (SHM) and TCP networking on
port 5000.
.PP
Authentication is performed through a master key provided via the
.B SPACEGL_KEY
environment variable or interactively at startup.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-version
Print version information and exit.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B SPACEGL_KEY
Master authentication key for the server session.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /usr/bin/spacegl_server
Server executable.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR spacegl_client (1),
.BR spacegl_server.sh (1),
.BR spacegl_3dview (1),
.BR spacegl_vulkan (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Nicola Taibi
